defaultOrganisations must include bad weather issue
defaults
default in their disaster recovery and Business Continuity planning.  Best practice guidelines should be prepared by leading trade associations for each sector and the Government should ensure they 
defaultare widely disseminated and adopted including within the public sector.  The cascading of decisions to close offices, allow staff home or to remain at home is critical and should be teste
defaultd 
defaultand updated on a regular basis
default in a similar way to fire or evacuation drills
