default or proposals to fit different tyres etc.  The IAM can see no case for the 
defaultcompulsory fitment of snow chain as 
defaultour winter maintenance procedures are not based on driving on hard packed snow.  Winter tyres can offer extra traction but the ‘hassle and cost’ of changing tyres on a seasonal basis is too high for most occasional bad weather episodes.  The tyre industry 
defaultshould continue to explore new rubber technology to 
defaultgive its all year tyres more useful winter properties.
