defaultThe IAM has no information on injuries and the number of incidents.  
default&#xa0;
defaultMany local authorities actually met their published targets for snow clearance but the public as a whole have little understandin
defaultg of winter maintenance priorities and often felt helpless and abandoned.   
default&#xa0;
defaultCouncils must be more explicit on how long they will take to
default clear side roads and footpaths and what the priorities are and the ‘order’ of clearance
default.
default  
default&#xa0;
defaultPoor footpath clearance can lead to 
defaultpedestrian injuries, 
defaultisolation and less inclination to attempt journeys which may actually be possible if main roads are accessible.  
