defaultA
default 
defaultnew approach which encourages m
defaultore personal responsibility for footpath cleaning 
defaultby local residents/shopkeepers/businesses
default,
default combined with a higher priority for local salt bins and a clearer timetable of footpath clearance would be the most effective way forward.  Urban myths regarding the law on personal liability due to snow clearing 
defaultshould be addressed as a matter of priority and local guidelines agreed and communicated to house holders and businesses.
