defaultThe latest developments in Ice alert, snow clearing equipment and chemicals should be monitored but the I
defaultA
defaultM is unaware of 
defaultany 
defaultnew thinking in winter maintenan
defaultce policy as a whole that would revolutionise our approach.  
defaultIn our view the most important area for technological advances would be techniques that do not require the passage of traffic to ‘work in’ salt and the ability to clear roads and deal with large 
defaultnumbers of stranded motorists at the same time.
default&#xa0;
defaultRoad user behaviour in Scandinavia does suggest that additional training in dealing with ice and snow can lead to over confidence and a rise in serious collisions. 
default&#xa0;
defaultQuick, reliable and personalised/localise
defaultd 
defaultinformation
default in an often fast changing weather situation is the key.  Access to more CCTV cameras off the trunk road network would help to give real time information on what is actually happening at key pints on the network.
